name: KALAMINA
description:
"You're not horrified enough to call it the limit of death but you can't turn a blind eye to beauty, like calamine."

Kalamina is a combination of words between Kala, which means Scorpio in Indonesian and Mina is Pisces, a representation of our respective births.
